snippet.title: Townseek 🦈 Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Whales And Games are teaming up with Super Rare Originals to bring Townseek to PC and Consoles!

Wishlist now: https://bit.ly/3jnZU80

Embark on a journey across the world of Explora and discover the lost legacy of Sir Reginald Sharkingston! Discover exotic landmarks, trade with faraway towns, fish, mine, and farm as you complete your journal and make a name for yourself!

Play the Townseek demo during Steam NextFest from 6th February-13th February!

- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
